♪My heart is locked up, never free♪

3
00:00:25,260 --> 00:00:34,420
♪Sometimes I go with it, spinning like a top♪

4
00:00:35,060 --> 00:00:44,300
♪No one to tell my secrets to, so I stay silent♪

5
00:00:47,700 --> 00:00:54,620
♪Loud is the echo I buried deep♪

6
00:00:57,300 --> 00:01:03,700
♪How I crave a single reply♪

7
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:08,660
♪Lonely souls are sand in the wind♪

8
00:01:09,260 --> 00:01:13,620
♪With nowhere to settle♪

9
00:01:13,980 --> 00:01:18,460
♪Broken all over, yet my heart won't give♪

10
00:01:19,020 --> 00:01:24,220
♪Like a flower blooming in a crack of stone♪

11
00:01:24,420 --> 00:01:28,980
[Loving Strangers]

12
00:01:29,020 --> 00:01:33,940
[Episode 27]

13
00:01:36,590 --> 00:01:37,210
Jiaqi.

14
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,570
I found Zhou Yu'an.

15
00:01:39,310 --> 00:01:39,900
That's great!

16
00:01:40,230 --> 00:01:40,980
Is she alright?

17
00:01:41,510 --> 00:01:42,100
She's fine.

18
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,380
Tell her not to worry too much.

19
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,290
I've consulted a lawyer.

20
00:01:47,150 --> 00:01:49,100
In her case, she's considered an accomplice.

21
00:01:49,350 --> 00:01:51,100
If the victim forgives her,

22
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,740
she might avoid punishment.

23
00:01:53,350 --> 00:01:53,980
My lawyer friend

24
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:54,930
is very experienced.

25
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,260
Don't worry.

26
00:01:58,070 --> 00:01:59,570
All this started because of me.

27
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:01,540
I want to make it up to her.

28
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:19,130
There's a kid named Liu Mingzhe.

29
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,220
Is he your friend?

30
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:23,570
What happened to him?

31
00:02:24,630 --> 00:02:25,450
Pang Jian called the police.

32
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:28,060
He's at the police station, cooperating with the investigation.

33
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:30,660
But don't worry too much.

34
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,690
Yijun has found a lawyer.

35
00:02:33,150 --> 00:02:33,980
She's already consulted.

36
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:36,500
It should be fine.

37
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,260
Once you're discharged,

38
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:44,370
we'll go visit Grandma.

39
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,870
After visiting Grandma,

40
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,610
I'll go with you to the police station.

41
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,100
We'll tell everything.

42
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,290
We've been using my phone

43
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:57,940
to keep in touch with you.

44
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,410
Didn't you listen in?

45
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,980
Since you knew I was listening in,

46
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:07,570
how could I keep doing that?

47
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,730
Don't you hate me at all,

48
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:20,260
for all the things I did?

49
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,100
No. Because I understand you.

50
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,570
If you truly understand someone,

51
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,780
no matter what they do,

52
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:33,340
you can accept it.

53
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,660
I love hearing your voice.

54
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,500
I can't die now.

55
00:03:44,590 --> 00:03:46,050
And those words from you.

56
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,660
Nothing's a big deal.

57
00:03:53,750 --> 00:03:54,610
Even your footsteps,

58
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,890
your sighs, I love them all.

59
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:06,290
It feels like I'm seeing for the first time...

60
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,290
what a person should be.

61
00:04:27,340 --> 00:04:29,140
[Galaxy Tavern]

62
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,610
You're here.

63
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:41,660
Let her stay with you for a couple of days.

64
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:42,610
It won't be too long.

65
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,730
No problem.

66
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,020
The longer, the better.

67
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:47,220
Give me the baggage.

68
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,370
I'll take it in.

69
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:53,490
I'll come pick you up tomorrow morning.

70
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:56,370
Uh...

71
00:04:58,920 --> 00:04:59,660
the recordings...

72
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:01,460
I'll delete them later.

73
00:05:07,510 --> 00:05:08,290
Get some good rest.

74
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:33,340
Why don't you ask me

75
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:34,660
why I came back?

76
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,290
Seeing you here,

77
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,610
I'm so happy.

78
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,100
Having someone accompany me to sleep

79
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:47,810
feels really nice.

80
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,370
I haven't had a proper sleep

81
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,170
in a long time.

82
00:06:12,940 --> 00:06:18,620
♪Trapped behind a window, far from joy♪

83
00:06:18,940 --> 00:06:24,220
♪I've grown used to swallowing my sadness alone♪

84
00:06:25,860 --> 00:06:27,820
♪I keep walking, lonely♪

85
00:06:28,860 --> 00:06:32,180
♪Is there a place where I can fall back?♪

86
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:42,700
♪We all have our reasons for being worn down...♪

87
