♪Like raindrops finding their way to a river♪

92
00:07:12,420 --> 00:07:15,820
♪I want to be with you♪

93
00:07:16,300 --> 00:07:22,460
♪Two souls in sync♪

94
00:07:23,620 --> 00:07:26,380
♪Darkness meets the light♪

95
00:07:26,740 --> 00:07:30,380
♪When heavy downpours fall on the world♪

96
00:07:31,140 --> 00:07:37,740
♪You walk with me through it♪

97
00:07:39,340 --> 00:07:42,180
♪I want to be with you♪

98
00:07:43,100 --> 00:07:45,260
♪When the world is in a hustle...♪

99
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,170
Why are you crying?

100
00:07:51,340 --> 00:07:54,900
♪I want to be with you...♪

101
00:07:56,750 --> 00:07:57,460
Because...

102
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,220
it is ending?

103
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:05,220
♪Once again, we believe in clear skies♪

104
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:26,860
[Galaxy Tavern]

105
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:39,770
Zhiyuan...

106
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,340
Actually, I really regret it.

107
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,180
That day,

108
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,010
you were here.

109
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,850
You told Jiaqi

110
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,650
you weren't happy,

111
00:09:55,670 --> 00:09:56,730
and you wanted to run away.

112
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:00,420
Actually, I heard it.

113
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:05,130
But I interrupted you.

114
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,730
Because I was really scared,

115
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:11,980
scared of hearing

116
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,980
an answer I couldn't bear.

117
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,770
But I never imagined

118
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:21,420
I'd really never get the chance

119
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,250
to know that answer.

120
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,340
All these years,

121
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,300
I've been waiting,

122
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,730
waiting for you to come back,

123
00:10:35,630 --> 00:10:37,300
waiting for you to tell me

124
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,700
why you're not happy.

125
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:44,890
But sometimes,

126
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,010
I wonder...

127
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,370
no matter where you are now,

128
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,490
has escaping all of this

129
00:10:58,270 --> 00:10:59,460
really made you happy

130
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,770
and truly free?

131
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,730
Maybe then,

132
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:10,180
I should let you go.

133
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:20,890
Tao Zhiyuan,

134
00:11:22,630 --> 00:11:23,490
today,

135
00:11:24,670 --> 00:11:26,060
I want to tell you,

136
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,650
I've decided to let go.

137
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,130
You and your answer

138
00:11:33,270 --> 00:11:34,730
can no longer trap me.

139
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:39,770
Let's break up!

140
00:12:25,670 --> 00:12:26,370
Tao Zhiyuan...

141
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:28,850
Goodbye.

142
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:54,700
I'd wanted to treat you to a proper meal,

143
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,940
but you never agreed.

144
00:12:58,550 --> 00:12:59,180
Today,

145
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,700
you suddenly came

146
00:13:02,390 --> 00:13:03,130
to see me.

147
00:13:03,550 --> 00:13:04,130
Look.

148
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,300
You've suffered.

149
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,370
You've gone through all this,

150
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,820
and still need to say it yourself.

151
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:21,460
You really...

152
00:13:22,910 --> 00:13:23,850
are something.

153
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:27,530
You actually told me...

154
00:13:29,150 --> 00:13:30,370
you want to leave.

155
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,650
After all, this matter

156
00:13:35,390 --> 00:13:37,370
was caused by Gu Chen, me and my wife.

157
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:39,940
I think

158
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:40,890
I should leave.

159
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,250
And this position

160
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,700
was originally Pang Jian's.

161
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,850
You don't need to worry about that.

162
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,460
I still hope

163
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,940
you'll carefully consider

164
00:13:53,670 --> 00:13:54,460
resigning.

165
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,770
Sorry, Chairman.

166
00:14:01,870 --> 00:14:02,460
Understood.

167
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:04,850
As for Pang Jian,

168
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:08,010
I'll reinstate him as Vice GM.

169
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,730
And I'll invite him for a meal,

170
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,700
letting him plead

171
00:14:13,630 --> 00:14:14,490
on Zhou Yu'an's behalf.

172
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:17,010
Thank you, Chairman.

173
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:23,610
Hello.

174
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:35,100
The sunshine is so warm today.

175
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:38,890
Spring is coming.

176
00:14:41,630 --> 00:14:45,700
I've never felt

177
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:52,130
so happy before.

178
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:15,100
Thank you

179
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:22,250
for being my granddaughter.

180
00:16:21,150 --> 00:16:22,220
Looking at you like this,

181
00:16:24,670 --> 00:16:26,220
it feels like a different person.

182
00:16:37,790 --> 00:16:38,610
Grandma said

183
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:41,460
she will always bless you.

184
00:17:08,740 --> 00:17:11,740
[Galaxy Tavern]

185
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:30,530
How is Grandma?

186
00:17:34,550 --> 00:17:36,090
I'll take you to see the lawyer now.

187
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:37,810
Don't worry.

188
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:39,530
Just tell the truth

189
00:17:39,590 --> 00:17:40,460
you know.

190
00:17:43,110 --> 00:17:43,570
Let's go.

191
00:17:55,620 --> 00:18:02,100
[Police]

192
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:03,700
Yu'an,

193
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:05,210
this is my good friend,

194
00:18:05,210 --> 00:18:06,020
Lawyer Fang.

195
00:18:06,640 --> 00:18:07,530
This is Zhou Yu'an.

196
00:18:10,830 --> 00:18:11,370
Don't worry.

197
00:18:11,550 --> 00:18:12,420
I'll do my best.

198
00:18:14,270 --> 00:18:14,810
Go ahead.

199
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:17,620
Let's go.

200
00:18:29,620 --> 00:18:32,340
[Renhetong Pawnshop]

201
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:39,010
You three will hold him down.

202
00:18:39,550 --> 00:18:41,460
You'll retrieve everything from the computer.

203
00:18:42,030 --> 00:18:42,530
Understood.

204
00:18:58,270 --> 00:18:58,810
Boss,

205
00:18:59,790 --> 00:19:00,730
the hard drive is gone.

206
00:19:13,620 --> 00:19:15,860
[Delivery Station]

207
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:24,290
He has a 2G phone.

208
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:27,380
The phone only has one contact number.

209
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:30,730
That number

210
00:19:32,030 --> 00:19:33,290
is Director Jiang's wife's.

211
00:19:37,310 --> 00:19:38,140
Anything else?

212
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:46,140
So I understood

213
00:19:46,510 --> 00:19:47,180
why he wanted

214
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:48,460
to get Director Jiang out.

215
00:19:50,310 --> 00:19:51,570
He promised to give me money,

216
00:19:51,720 --> 00:19:52,490
fifty thousand yuan per person.

217
00:19:54,070 --> 00:19:55,730
He wanted me to get rid of those two people.

218
00:19:58,480 --> 00:19:59,730
She found my weakness,

219
00:20:00,310 --> 00:20:01,570
telling me

220
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:02,900
she knew

221
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:04,010
why I wanted to get rid of Jiang Jiaqi.

222
00:20:04,310 --> 00:20:05,180
She said she could help me

223
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:06,980
get rid of Pang Jian and Jiang Jiaqi,

224
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:08,730
fifty thousand yuan each.

225
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:10,900
But why should I trust her?

226
00:20:12,270 --> 00:20:12,730
I didn't agree.

227
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:15,420
But later, she found me again.

228
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,180
She told me

229
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:18,010
she was behind Pang Jian's situation.

230
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:19,620
She asked me to pay her.

231
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,730
How could I pay her?

232
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:26,010
People like her are terrifying.

233
00:20:26,350 --> 00:20:27,570
I'm better off avoiding her.

234
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:30,180
Knowing full well Pang Jian was tricked,

235
00:20:30,750 --> 00:20:32,010
why didn't you call the police?

236
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:34,570
Sir,

237
00:20:34,570 --> 00:20:35,460
at that time,

238
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:38,140
I was facing re-election.

239
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:39,860
If I called the police,

240
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:41,860
the company would surely suspect

241
00:20:42,030 --> 00:20:42,620
my involvement.

242
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:46,180
He said he'd give me money.

243
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:50,730
He asked me to keep listening in on Director Jiang,

244
00:20:53,070 --> 00:20:54,290
and also to spread rumors

245
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,900
to make sure he couldn't escape.

246
00:20:57,880 --> 00:20:59,010
I had her do it?

247
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:02,490
Well...

248
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:03,140
did she tell you

249
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,900
she liked Jiang Jiaqi?

250
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:07,050
You received cash,

251
00:21:07,590 --> 00:21:09,420
and the audio recordings are missing.

252
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:12,010
So do you have any evidence

253
00:21:12,070 --> 00:21:12,730
that Gu Chen instructed you?

254
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,330
You can apply to investigate

255
00:21:15,590 --> 00:21:17,010
Gu Chen's 2G phone

256
00:21:17,160 --> 00:21:18,460
and my client's call records

257
00:21:18,510 --> 00:21:19,250
and messages.

258
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,290
But the other party denies

259
00:21:21,310 --> 00:21:22,290
having this phone.

260
00:21:23,110 --> 00:21:23,980
We have witnesses,

261
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:25,010
who can prove

262
00:21:25,070 --> 00:21:26,140
the existence of this phone.

263
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:38,810
Hello?

264
00:21:39,720 --> 00:21:40,810
We're on our way back.

265
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:42,380
I'll take her to Chu Dan.

266
00:21:43,270 --> 00:21:43,810
How's it going?

267
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:46,490
The recordings are gone.

268
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:47,380
It's a bit of a hassle.

269
00:21:48,030 --> 00:21:49,380
They need to check the call records.

270
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:51,010
By the way,

271
00:21:51,270 --> 00:21:52,700
how's the communication with Pang Jian?

272
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:54,250
He's willing to write a letter of understanding,

273
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:55,490
promising not to pursue it.

274
00:21:56,750 --> 00:21:57,570
That's great.

275
00:21:58,750 --> 00:22:00,050
Okay, let's talk later.

276
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:08,490
Why did you

277
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:10,620
delete the chat records?

278
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:13,490
They mentioned

279
00:22:13,590 --> 00:22:14,620
your situation with Gu Chen.

280
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:18,250
It will make Jiang Jiaqi suffer.

281
00:22:24,960 --> 00:22:25,810
Every time

282
00:22:25,830 --> 00:22:27,140
Jiang Jiaqi calls you,

283
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:31,290
one thing's the warmest:

284
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:37,620
want me to bring you something?

285
00:23:05,340 --> 00:23:08,300
[Galaxy Tavern]

286
00:23:31,240 --> 00:23:31,830
Jiaqi!

287
00:23:31,830 --> 00:23:33,010
Jiaqi? Look who's here!

288
00:23:35,110 --> 00:23:35,570
Don't worry!

289
00:23:35,590 --> 00:23:37,140
We've taken good care of Yu'an!

290
00:23:39,350 --> 00:23:40,460
Jiaqi's now Vice GM.

291
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:41,380
